# Copilot Configuration File

# Rules
# 1. Do not change function names.
# 2. Only modify comments when requested.
# 3. Avoid touching specific files unless explicitly instructed.
# 4. Follow user-defined coding conventions strictly.
# 5. Do not modify any comments immediately following "///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////". This is the most critical rule.

# Example of user-defined conventions:
# - Comments must start with capitalized verbs in third-person singular.
# - Do not refactor code unless explicitly requested.

# File-specific rules
# - Do not modify Texture.Draw\System\Drawing\HSVColor.cs unless explicitly instructed.

# Coding Conventions
# |No|Target|Notation|Remarks|
# |:--|:--|:--|:--|
# |-|Class|PascalCase|Context|
# |-|Delegate|PascalCase|Action|
# |-|Interface|I+PascalCase|IContext|
# |-|Enum|PascalCase|Code|
# |-|Annotation(Attribute)|PascalCase|Service|
# |-|Public Method|PascalCase|GetHoge|
# |-|Public Static Method|PascalCase|GetHoge|
# |-|Property|PascalCase Å¶Unity:CamelCase|HogeValue or hogeValue|
# |-|Protected Method|CamelCase|getHoge|
# |-|Protected Static Method|CamelCase|getHoge|
# |-|Private Method|CamelCase|getHoge|
# |-|Private Static Method|CamelCase|getHoge|
# |-|Argument|CamelCase|hogeValue|
# |-|Field|Underscore + Snake_Case|_hoge_value|
# |-|Local Variable|Snake_Case|hoge_value|
# |-|Constant|Upper_Snake_Case|HOGE_VALUE|

# Additional Notes
# - Always confirm before making changes to critical files.
# - Respect user preferences and coding style.
